{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "c93d78da-45d5-4293-80e7-c19d63722b9d", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/c93d78da-45d5-4293-80e7-c19d63722b9d@1.pkg/1772597689589/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597689996", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/c93d78da-45d5-4293-80e7-c19d63722b9d@1.pkg/1772597689589/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597689996"}, "identifier": "c93d78da-45d5-4293-80e7-c19d63722b9d", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>本题考查共建美好集体。</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>甲仅从时间投入和获奖结果衡量活动价值，忽视了集体活动中团队协作、能力提升等重要意义，不符合题意。​</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>乙关注到集体活动中团队凝聚力的增强和过程中的收获，符合题意。​</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>丙缺乏团队责任感，存在推诿指责的心态，不利于集体团结。​</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>丁现了积极进取的态度和集体成长意识，体现了对集体荣誉的重视和共同进步的追求，符合题意。​</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>综上，符合题意的是乙和丁，答案选 B。</b></span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）某班参与学校 &ldquo;班级文化展示&rdquo; 活动，同学们精心准备却未获得奖项。校园小记者现场采访时，该班同学发表了不同看法：​</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>甲：花了这么多时间准备，没获奖太不值了！​</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>乙：虽然没获奖，但大家一起策划、排练的过程很开心，班级更团结了。​</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>丙：都是因为个别同学不够用心，才导致我们失败的。​</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>丁：其他班级的展示很精彩，我们要学习他们的优点，下次继续加油！​</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>小记者要编辑 &ldquo;弘扬集体精神&rdquo; 的新闻稿，你认为应该选用的采访素材是（ ）​</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（改编）某班参与学校 “班级文化展示” 活动，同学们精心准备却未获得奖项。校园小记者现场采访时，该班同学发表了不同看法：甲：花了这么多时间准备，没获奖太不值了！乙：虽然没获奖，但大家一起策划、排练的过程很开心，班级更团结了。丙：都是因为个别同学不够用心，才导致我们失败的。丁：其他班级的展示很精彩，我们要学习他们的优点，下次继续加油！小记者要编辑 “弘扬集体精神” 的新闻稿，你认为应该选用的采访素材", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/c93d78da-45d5-4293-80e7-c19d63722b9d@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754977961023", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>甲和丙 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>乙和丁 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>甲和丁 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": tr